description: Recently sold: $304,000. Everything your looking for in a year round home with stunning sunsets, gradual slope down to the lake shore, sandy beach, great fishing. Remodeled 1695 SF 2BR/2BThs, tongue & groove vaulted ceilings and walls, opening living space, modern kitchen, living room w/fireplace, patio doors opened to the 3 season porch/open deck. Finnish sauna at water's edge/boat house/dock/fire ring. Large Quaint 790 SF Log Guest Cabin, Home Office/Fiber optic HS Internet/1 BR/1BTH/new 100 amp, cathedral ceiling/fireplace/open kitchen-living room/large wrap around deck. Both properties have a beautiful lake view. Could be used for summer rental. New septic/electrical service/etc.. The yard has been newly landscaped with additional trees/shrubs/rock gardens. All of this is located half way between Virginia/Duluth. Relax and Enjoy living on one of the great northern Minnesota Lakes.

Recently sold: $396,893. Beautiful Lake Home on quiet Lake Nichols. 106 feet of shoreline on 435 acre lake. Short commute to Duluth and Virginia. Second driveway to access shoreline.  Newly updated kitchen with granite countertops, stainless appliances, with built ins in dining area. Master suite includes huge walk in closet with laundry area. Master bath has double vanity with granite countertops, jetted tub, and large tiled shower. Huge deck off great room overlooking lake and private yard. Deck off master bedroom also overlooking lake. Office/den on main floor. Lower level includes in floor heat, new wood flooring, second kitchen, family room, two more bedrooms all overlooking lake.  There are two newly updated bathrooms and a second laundry in lower level along with a bonus room . Home sits on a 106X290ft. beautifully landscaped lot. Blacktop circular driveway. Shed for extra storage. 2 docks included. Call for appointment to view home.  $399,900
